column1: Comments: Capture of the DoS injection attack against the lab system in ASCII mode. Lab is set into automode
column2: and the dos_injection is started around 1306790669
column4: and then is stopped at 1306791393. The system recovers. USB0 is what the master receives
column5: USB2 is what the slave receives. This capture was made with tap cables between the PLCs and their respective radios.
